    <title>SAP CodeJam HANA ML (Istanbul, TR) 2023-12 Recap</title>
    <updated>2023-12-19T15:19:12.780000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Vitaliy-R</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/183</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Last Saturday we had the Getting Started with &lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/Machine+Learning/pd-p/240174591523510321507492941674121" class="lia-product-mention" data-product="2-1"&gt;Machine Learning&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;using &lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/SAP+HANA/pd-p/73554900100700000996" class="lia-product-mention" data-product="639-1"&gt;SAP HANA&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and &lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/Python/pd-p/f220d74d-56e2-487e-8e6c-a8cb3def2378" class="lia-product-mention" data-product="126-1"&gt;Python&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;in İstanbul, Turkey kindly hosted by Sovos and organized by &lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/99"&gt;@huseyindereli&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="IMG_7285.jpeg" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/51637i4E78A3D03ABFF290/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="IMG_7285.jpeg" alt="IMG_7285.jpeg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Explaining how an embedded Machine Learning fits into the SAP HANA Cloud's big picture:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="IMG_7272.jpeg" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/51638iF3591526862B2F04/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="IMG_7272.jpeg" alt="IMG_7272.jpeg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;Yummy breakfast for the participants:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="IMG_7269.jpeg" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/51639iE9EF015BC6241F23/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="IMG_7269.jpeg" alt="IMG_7269.jpeg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;It was great to meet my dear friends and SAP Mentors&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/8060"&gt;@abdulbasit&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/144072"&gt;@ridvan_polat&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;again!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="IMG_7270.jpeg" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/51640i5CD892B1F025B888/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="IMG_7270.jpeg" alt="IMG_7270.jpeg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;Working hard on the exercises.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="IMG_7281.jpeg" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/51641i51A90843812C24C6/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="IMG_7281.jpeg" alt="IMG_7281.jpeg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="f54e35ef-6fe2-41a4-825c-1a8e2c9df5c0.jpeg" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/51643i19D888F43FE1B897/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="f54e35ef-6fe2-41a4-825c-1a8e2c9df5c0.jpeg" alt="f54e35ef-6fe2-41a4-825c-1a8e2c9df5c0.jpeg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;And some &lt;EM&gt;baklava&lt;/EM&gt; for humans at the end: to recharge after an exhausting day with the AI &lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":robot_face:"&gt;🤖&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="IMG_7288.jpeg" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/51642iBA5DBD5D27AE62DE/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="IMG_7288.jpeg" alt="IMG_7288.jpeg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;If you are interested in hosting an SAP CodeJam, all the details can be found&amp;nbsp;in the post &lt;A href="https://blogs.sap.com/2023/08/02/getting-started-with-machine-learning-using-sap-hana-as-a-new-sap-codejam-topic/" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;“Getting Started with Machine Learning using SAP HANA” as the SAP CodeJam topic&lt;/A&gt;.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;PS. No stay in Istanbul without having some yummy &lt;EM&gt;mezes&lt;/EM&gt; &lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":face_savoring_food:"&gt;😋&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="IMG_7305.jpeg" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/51644i94E10CAD3F3D20FE/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="IMG_7305.jpeg" alt="IMG_7305.jpeg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;...but watch out for the meal prices at the airport &lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":grimacing_face:"&gt;😬&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="IMG_7431.jpeg" style="width: 300px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/51645i26D2C2645A0BAED1/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="IMG_7431.jpeg" alt="IMG_7431.jpeg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam-blog-posts/sap-codejam-hana-ml-istanbul-tr-2023-12-recap/ba-p/308597"/>
    <published>2023-12-19T15:19:12.780000+01:00</published>
