  <entry>
    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/getting-started-with-machine-learning-using-sap-hana-and-python-vilnius-lt/ev-p/13592988</id>
    <title>🇱🇹 Getting Started with Machine Learning using SAP HANA and Python (Vilnius, LT)</title>
    <updated>2024-02-02T16:22:54.680000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Vitaliy-R</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/183</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;This&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://groups.community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/gh-p/code-jam" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;SAP CodeJam&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;event is on the topic of&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Getting&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;Started with Machine Learning using SAP HANA&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;and Python&lt;/SPAN&gt;. You do not need to have any background in the topic, but a lot of curiosity!&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;You'll become acquainted with how embedded Machine Learning in SAP HANA can be used to build ML models. In working through this CodeJam you'll also become familiar with how the SAP Business Application Studio can be used to work with Jupyter notebooks.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;This is a&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;free&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;in-person event&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;and is planned for&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Friday, 26th of April 2024 in&amp;nbsp;Vilnius, Lithuania&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;from 10:00 to 17:00 EET (UTC+2)&lt;/SPAN&gt;.&amp;nbsp;The language of the event and the content will be in English.&amp;nbsp;The instructor is a&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://developers.sap.com/developer-advocates.html" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;Developer Advocate&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;Vitaliy Rudnytskiy&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;There are essential prerequisites that&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;must be completed by every attendee, before arriving at the event location&lt;/STRONG&gt;. They are documented here:&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://github.com/SAP-samples/hana-ml-py-codejam/blob/main/prerequisites.md#prerequisites" target="_self" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener"&gt;https://github.com/SAP-samples/hana-ml-py-codejam/blob/main/prerequisites.md&lt;/A&gt;.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;The event is being&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;hosted by Justas Brazauskas&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;and&lt;STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;Accenture&lt;/STRONG&gt; at&amp;nbsp;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;FONT size="2"&gt;UNIQ building, 6th floor &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;FONT size="2"&gt;A. Goštauto g. 12A &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;FONT size="2"&gt;01108 Vilnius&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Please reach out to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/833469"&gt;@justbraz&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;if you have any questions about the logistics.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Note that spaces are limited: we can only accommodate&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;25 attendees&lt;/STRONG&gt;.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;EM&gt;For more information on SAP CodeJam events, to ask questions, and to chat with your fellow attendees, head over to the&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://groups.community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/gh-p/code-jam" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;SAP CodeJam group&lt;/A&gt;.&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/getting-started-with-machine-learning-using-sap-hana-and-python-vilnius-lt/ev-p/13592988"/>
    <published>2024-02-02T16:22:54.680000+01:00</published>
  </entry>
